		        </tr>
		        <tr>
			        <td valign="top" class="tableCell"><span id="speakerBioLabel">James C. Smith has worked in the games industry for 10 years and has focused on the downloadable casual games segment since 2001. James is a founding partner of Reflexive Entertainment, which develops quality casual games and manages the Reflexive Arcade distribution network which empowers affiliates to distribute over 500 casual games. As a producer at Reflexive, James led the development teams of many commercially successful causal games including Big Kahuna Reef, Big Kahuna Words, Ricochet Xtreme (a.k.a. Rebound), and Ricochet Lost Worlds. James also contributed to Reflexive's other games including Wik & the Fable of Souls, Swarm, & Mosaic: Tomb of Mystery. Many of these games are available for Windows, Mac, PalmOS, WindowsCE, Xbox, Xbox 360, and cell phones. James also contributes to publications of the IGDA casual games SIG and he runs GameSalesCharts.com, which tracks sales trends in major casual game portals.</span></td>
